    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and pride of ownership without the showroom price tag. The exterior presents beautifully, with a deep gloss to the paint and only minor, age-appropriate stone chips that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin has been smoke-free and meticulously kept; the leather is supple, the carpets are clean, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in top form, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two keys, and a comprehensive folder of service receipts.",
